  13 Siong7-Hai2 E5 U7-Sim2 
  Keh-jit8 8 tiam2, chiu7 ti7 Siong7-hai2 e5 te7-hng hoat-iN7 khui-teng5 kong-phoaN3. Hit-si5 mng7 hoan7-choe7-jin5 kui2-ku3, chiu7 kio3 Hok-choan3 chhut-lai5 cho3 cheng3-jin5, liam5-piN bu5-ki5-tou5-heng5 soan-ko3. Tu2 beh pi3-teng5 e5 si5, u7 chit8-e5 lang5 hut-jian5 khia7 khi2-lai5 kio3 cheng3-lang5 ban7-chiah soaN3. Kiam2-chhat-koaN tu2 beh kio3 chiang2 sim2-phoaN3-tiuN2 e5 lang5 hoah i tiam7-tiam7, chit8-e5 khoaN3, to-si7 choan5-kok ti7-beng5 e5 tek8-bu7 tham3-cheng Chhoa3 Thian-pheng5 sin-seN, chiu7 tai7-ke koh che7 loh8-lai5 thiaN i kong2. Hit-si5 Tan5 Hok-choan5 e5 bin7 chit8-chun7-chheN, chit8-chun7-ang5, long2 gong7-khi3. Tek8-bu7 tham3-cheng chiu7 kong2, Liat8-ui7 kin-a2-jit8 chit-e5 cheng3-jin5, goan5-lai5 m7-si7 ho7-cho3 Tan5 Hok-choan5, si7 Tan5 Ek-sam, tai7-ke thiaN chit8-e7 toa7-kiaN; in-ui7 Tan5 Ek-sam Lian-hoe-ti5 e5 su7-kiaN7, chiah-ku2 tiaN7-ti7 sin-bun5-choa2 khoaN3-kiN3, sou2-i2 mia5 chin thau3, (choe7 teh lang5) theng3-chiong3 kang2 chheng-lang5 chu2-bak8 khoaN3 i. Ek-sam chit8-si5 chin kiaN, bin7 long2 piN3 si2-lang5 sek. Tek8-bu7 tham3-cheng chiu7 chiap-soa3 kong2, chit-lang5 chiu7-si7 sin-bun5-choa2 sou2 ki3 Lian-hoe-ti5 su7-kiaN7 e5 lang5, goa2 thiaN i chau2 tui3 Siong7-hai2 lai5, siong5-se3 tham3-cha kok hong-bin7 e5 kheh-koan2. Kau3 Kun5-eng koan2 u7 chha5-tioh8 chit-e5 ki5-koai3 e5 su7-kiaN7, sou2-ki2 thiau5-kang lai5 pong5-theng, kau3-ui7 ko2-jian5 khoaN3 i ti7-chia. Sou2-i2 chit-tiap8 ai3 chu7-an2-ni lau5 i ti7-chia, ban7-chiah the3-tiuN5. Kong2 liau2-au7 chiu7 chin3-cheng5 oa2-khi3 tui3 chhiu2 ka7 i khan teh, ia7 chhiaN2 cheng3-lang5 si3-soaN3, ia7 in-ui7 i u7 tng khu-tiuN2 e5 chit, sou2-i2 m7-ai3 ti7 tng-tiuN5 liah8 i. 
  Hit-am3 tek8-piat8 Chhoa3 sin-seN tit-chiap hoah the3 kiam2-chhat-koaN kap su-ki3. Kan-ta ko3-jin5 cho3 chhin-chhiuN7 peng5-iu2 lai5 teh tham3 i e5 hi-sit8. In-ui7 Chhoa3 tek8-bu7 chin tong5-cheng5 i, chai i si7 cho3 khu-tiuN2, beng5-bong7-lang5, sou2-i2 chin ai3 kiu3 i. Chiu7 mng7 i kong2, Ek-sam li2 ui3-chiaN2-iuN7 thai3 to5-chau2? Goa2 m7-si7 to5-chau2, si7 ui7 u7 su7-kou3 lai5 Siong7-hai2. Li2 na7 m7-si7 chun5 to5-chau2 e5 i3-su3, an2-choaN2 tiam3 lu2-koan2 thai2 tioh8 oaN7-mia5? Goa2 to ai3 pi7 hiam5-gi5. Ai3 pi7 siaN2-mih8 hiam5-gi5? KiaN lang5 phe-pheng5 goa2 chhoa7 Gek8-chu chhut-lai5. Chhoa7 Gek8-chu chhut-lai5 kiam2 u7 saN2 iau3-kin2, thai3 tioh8 oaN7-mia5? Goa2 siuN7 li2 m7-si7 ui7 an2-ni, si7 u7 khah chhim e5 ke3-oe7. Bo5, bo5, Li2 chaiN2-iuN7 khi3 be2 lou7-chio3? Goa2 to siuN7 beh koe3 goa7-kok. Li2 thau5-tu2-a2 kong2 si7 u7 tam7-poh8 tai7-chi3 lai5-kau3 Siong7-hai2 na7-tiaN7, ia7 chit-tiap8 kong2 beh khi3 goa7-kok? Goa2 to lai5 chia, chiah siuN7 ai3 khi3. Ia7 siuN7 ai3 khi3 thai2 bo5 eng7 li2 e5 mia5 khi3 kip-lou7-chio7, thai2 eng7 pat8-e5 lang5 e5 mia5? An2-ni li2 si7 beh thau-chau2. TaN li2 na7 chun5-sim beh khi3 goa7-kok pan7 tai7-chi3 cho3 seng-li2, ia7 un2-tang3 u7 che7-chio2 e5 heng5-li2, heng5-li2 ti7 to2-ui7? Goa2 to bo5 khoan2 heng5-li2, an2-choaN bo5? To khoan2 be7-hu3. U7 sim2-mih8 su7 hou7 li2 khoan2 be7-hu3; KiaN hu3-chun5 be7-tioh8. Li2 na7 hiah chim-chiok kiaN hu7-chun5 be7-tioh8? ChaiN2-iuN7 bo5 liong7-cha2 pi7-pan7? Goa2 to hut-jian5 siuN7 beh chhut-goa7-e5. Li2 kiam2 m7-chai li2 si7 tng khu-tiuN2, tak8-jit8 ai3 chhut-sek8 pan7-su7, an2-choaN2 u7 tai7-chi3 tioh8 khi3 goa7-kok, bo5 liong7-cha2 the5-chhut khoat-khin5-kai3, ia7 beh chhut-hoat bo5 lang5 chai? An2-ni li2 un2-tang3 chun5 beh chau2-thoat sim2-mih8 choe7-chong7 e5 taN2-sng3, na7 bo5, chiu7 bo5 hiah chheN-kong5, ia7 hiah kau2-koai3 e5 pou7-sou3. Chin nge7-chhui3, long2 m7-jin7.
  Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 ka7 i sang3-loh8 u7-sim2 kaN-gak8. Ah! chit8-si3 lang5 long2 si7 ho2-mia7, kau3 kin-a2-jit8 tioh8 siu7 kaN-gak8, chit-me5 chin m7-goan7, chiap8-chiap8 siuN7 beh si2; m7-ku2 siuN7 m7-goan7, e7-ki3-tit goa2 cham3 Hui7-bi2 to na2-chun2 cham3 bo5 sim2-mih8 tioh8, koh goa2 m7-si7 chun5 phaiN2-i3 beh lai5 i si2, an2-ni goa2 na7 chu7-chin7 soah chu7 an2-ni hou7-lang5 kong2 cha-pou-kiaN2 ui3-su7, ia7 tai7-chi3 bo5-beng5 chiu7 kiaN kau3 si2. Ah! chit8-sim siuN7 beh kap i pian7 chit8-e7 ou-peh8, tui3 an2-ni chiu7 to2 loh8-khi3 khun3. Bak8-chiu kheh-khi3, chiu7 koh khoaN3 Hui7-bi2 khia7-ti7 bin7-cheng5, phiN7, bak8, chhui3 choan5 lou-kou5-moai5. Ah! chin kiaN, khah theng5-ti7 chhng5-cheng5 khah-theng5 ti7 chhng5-au7. Peh khi2-lai5 bak8-chiu thi2-khui iu7 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3, ka-ki7 siuN7 tek-khak si7 Hui7-bi2 piN3-kui2 beh lai5 liah8 i. Bak8-chiu kheh khi3 chiu7 koh lai5, tui3 an2-ni soah na2 chhin-chhiuN7 siau2-e5. Koh hoan5-lo2 bin5-a2-jit8 beh koh chit8-pian3 cheng3-sek e5 u7-sim2, soah khi2-kong5 e5 khoan2, kui-me5 peh khi2-lai5 loan7-loan7 kiaN5. 
