  14 Ui5-Gian5-Su 
  Mng7 kau3-chia, soa3 tiam7-tiam7 bo5-oe7, in-ui7 sim-bang5-bang5, soa3 be7-hiau2 in3. U7-sim2-koaN kong2, Li2 na7 m7 in3, chiu7 beh ka7 li2 cho3 su7-sit8 lai5 ke3-sang3 lah. Iu5-goan5 tiam7-tiam7, hit-me5 chiu7 ka7 i sang3-jip8 u7-sim2 kaN-pang5, koaiN-ti7 te7 4 ho7 sek. Keh cha2-khi3 beh tah cha2-chhia loh8-lai5 Lam5-kiaN, hu3 12 goeh8 chhe e5 kong-phoaN3, in-ui7 khah oan7, kiaN-liau2 na2 khi3 ni5-boe2 na2 bo5-eng5. Hit-me5 Ek-sam ka-ti7 e5 liong5-sim chu7-chek, hoan2-hoe2 i e5 chho3-gou7. Ah! kin-na2-jit8 goa2 si7 tong5-tong5 chit8-e5 u7 chu-keh e5 sin-su7, tioh8 lai5 siu7 koaiN-kaN, siu7 sim2-mng7, kiam2-chhai2 tioh8 kau3 si2-heng5 e5 te7-pou7, ia7 ti7 2, 3 jit8 cheng5 tui3 sin-bun5 ia7 khoaN3-tioh8 in lau7-bu2 tiau3-tau7 chu7-sat lai5 si2. Ah liong5-sim it-hoat kan-khou2, siuN7 kong2 goa2 kin-na2-jit8 e5 oah8, oah8-tit bo5 lou7-eng7. Koh siang7 kan-khou2, chiu7-si7 koh siuN7-kiN3 cheng5 i kap Hui7-bi2 e5 saN-thiaN3, khi2-thau5 i m7-ke3-i, ia7 i tit8-kiu5, ia7 tui3 jip8 i e5 chhu3-mng5, ia7 si7 chin koai, su7-su7 long2 si7 thun-lun2, un-jiu5 siong2-se3, ia7 kin-na2-jit8 e7 lai5 si2, koh si7 si2-ti7 hui-beng7. Ah! na2 siuN7 na2 m7-kam, koe3 Hui7-bi2 chin be7-tit-khi3. Chiu7 khui-siaN ka-ti7 hau2, ia7 ti7 kan-khou2 e5 kek8-thau5 chiu7 koh siuN7-tioh8 Siong7-te3, chiu7 kui7-loh8 ti7 gak8-pang5 e5 thou5-kha khui-siaN ki5-to2. Ah! Siong7-te3 ah, kiu3 leh ou3! Sim na2 kan-khou2. Chiu7 siuN7 koat-i3 beh chu7-chin7; in-ui7 na7 kau3 thiN-kng, to3-khi3 Lam5-kiaN, hia u7 chhin-chiaN5 peng5-iu2, un2-tang3 toa7 thi2-chhio3, khoaN3-khin.
  In-ui7 sin-chiuN7 u7 hai7-si2 bou2, khi3-si2 lau7-bu2, sit8-chai7 si7 put-hau3 e5 choe7-khoe, siuN7-liau2 bo5 bin7 thang kiN3-lang5. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 siuN7 beh thau2 khou3-toa3 khi2-lai5 chhui hou7 i si2. Au7-lai5 koh siuN7-tioh8 si2, si2-tit m7-tat8; in-ui7 ka-ti7 e5 sim-tiong bo5 10-hun kam-goan7, kong2 u7 hai7-si2 Hui7-bi2, in-ui7 goa2 to ki3-tit ka7 i cham3 bo5 sim2-mih8 tioh8, an2-choaN2 e7 lian3 loh8-khi3. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 ka7 kou3-kaN e5 lang5, tho2 chit8-te3 choa2 kap pit, chiu7 ka-ti7 cheng7-cheng7 phak-ti7 bin5-chhng5, lai5 sia2 chit8-tiuN ui5-gian5-chng7, au7-lai5 chiah beh lai5 si2. Sia2-kong2, Ah! Kau3-chia goa2 si7 chin kian3-siau3, si7 u7-choe7 e5 lang5; chong2-si7 Hui7-bi2 ah! goa2 e5 sim kau3-taN sit8-chai7 iau2-u7 chun5 thiaN3 li2 e5 sim, goa2 cheng5 e5 sou2-cho3 sit8-chai7 u7 toa7 chho3-gou7, goa2 chit-tiap8 koh siuN7-tioh8 lan2 cheng5 khi3 ban2 pek-hap8-hoe, a2-si7 cho3-hoe2 kou3 A-pa e5 phoa3-peN7, a2-si7 ti7 Lam5-iong5 e5 cheng5-heng5. Ah! goa2 chin-chiaN3 chai li2 si7 chin thiaN3-goa2. Goa2 chit-tiap8 na7 koh siuN7 tioh8 li2 e5 bin7,chin-chiaN3 tak8 si5 u7 ho5-peng5, thiaN3-thang3, thun-lun2, e5 khoan2-sit. Ah! lun7 jin5-keh, goa2 chin-chiaN3 m7-tat8-tioh8 li2. Li2 chin-chiaN3 si7 chin e5 Ki-tok-lu2-tou5, ia7 goa2 sit8-chai7 kong2, goa2 e5 sim m7-kaN2 be7-ki3-tit li2 e5 thiaN3-cheng5. Goa2 ia7 sit8-chai7 thiaN3-li2. Ah! mou5-kui2 e5 khui3-lat8 ah! Li2 chaiN2-iuN7 be5 goa2 kau3-ti7 chhim-kheN, ham7-hai7 goa2 kau3 chiah-chham2 ah! Ah! Siu3-chhun ah! Gek8-chu ah! Lin2 chin-chiaN3 si7 mou5-kui2 e5 khi3-khu7, hai7 goa2 kin-a2-jit8 kap goa2 sou2 chi3 chhin-ai3 e5 kut-tiong e5 kut bah-tiong e5 bah e5 Hui7-bi2 lai5 pun-khui. Ah! Hui7-bi2 ah! Li2 na7 ko2-jian5 thiaN3--goa2, kiu5 li2 sia3-bian2 goa2, the2-thiap goa2 chit8-si5 e5 chho3-gou7, tong5-cheng5 goa2 chin-sit8 e5 hoan2-hoe2. Ah! goa2 chin-chiaN3 tek-choe7 ti7 thiN kap tek-choe7 ti7 li2. Ah! Siong7-te3 ah, Li2 na7 sia3-bian2 kiu3 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5, kau3 ti7 li2 e5 kok, goa2 ti7-hia tek-khak beh koh tui3 sou2-thiaN3 e5 Hui7-bi2 jin7-chho3. Ah! Hit-si5 ti7-hia, goa2 beh koh eng2-oan2 kap i saN-thiaN3; Ah! goa2 sou2-thiaN3 e5 Hui7-bi2 ah! Li2 tioh8 sia3-bian2 goa2, li2 tioh8 the3 goa2 kiu5 Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2 goa2 hoan7 chhit-kai3 e5 choe7, i2-kip8 sou2-cho3 tak8-hang7 e5 m7-tioh8. Ah! lun7 li2 e5 si2, goa2 chin m7-kam, goa2 chin-chiaN3 bo5 chun5 hit-ho7 sim, goa2 khoaN3 goa2 that li2 bo5 tioh8. Chu2-ah, kiu5 Li2 kam3-chhat! 
  Sia2 kau3 chia, sim chin toa7 kan-khou2, khui-siaN hau2. Hut-jian5 khoaN3 thang-a2 mng7-goa7 chit8-e5 lang5 kiaN5-koe3, chin seng5 Hui7-bi2. Ah! Hui7-bi2 ah! Kin2 khui-mng5, jiok chhut-lai5. Hit-si5 si7 goeh8-am3-mi5 am3-bin5-bong, khi3 that-tioh8 chioh8-thau5 soah poah8-to2. Kau3-chia siong5-siong5 bo5 chiah8, hoan5-lo2, koh bat peN7 chiaN5 le2-pai3 ti7 kaN-gak8 e5 peN7-iN7, lang5 tu2 peN7 ho2 chin hi-jiok8, to2 loh8-khi3 soah nau2 pin5-hiat. Hit-si5 kiaN5-koe3 thang-a2-mng5 goa7 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 oa2-lai5 ka7 i chhah, hou7 i the-teh, teh ka7 i loah8, i bak8-chiu koh thi2-khui khoaN3, beng5-beng5 si7 Hui7-bi2 chiu7 khui-siaN kong2, Hui7-bi2 ah! Li2 kiam2 m7 si7 Hui7-bi2. TaN chit-tiap8 lan2 ti7 chia si7 hian7-se3, a2-si7 ng5-choaN5 ah! Lan2 taN si7 si2, a2 iau2 oah8 leh? Ek-sam ah! ChhiaN2 li2 an-sim, chia si7 chhau2-pou, tioh8 jip8-lai5 khi3 lai7-bin7. Hit-e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kio3 kou3-kaN-e5 lai5, tau3 chhah-jip8 gak8-pang5, hou7 i khun3 chiu7 chhut-khi3. 
